All about the new Avocado ceramide moisture barrier cleanser with @sarah_glow & @christine_glow 🥑

It’s official, @glowbyramon has the brightest eyes we’ve ever seen 🤩 He brought the brightening power to his eye area with the new Guava Vitamin C Bright-Eye Gel Cream, a gentle yet effective daily eye cream that helps brighten dark circles, depuffs, and and evens tone. When used consistently, the eye area is smoother, firmer, more hydrated, and more illuminated with a reduction in dark circles and puffiness. Bonus: its lightweight texture layers amazingly with makeup ✅ The formula absorbs quickly, creating a smooth and hydrated base that makes makeup go on like a dream. ✨⁠
Try it for yourself at @sephora @sephoracanada @sephoramiddleeast and coming soon to @sephorasg @sephorahk @sephoramy⁠
#GlowRecipe #CrueltyFree #GuavaEye⁠
How to treat dark circled with our new Guava Vit C Bright Eye Gel Cream

We wanted an eye cream that would brighten, depuff, and help our eye area look wide awake (even when we were running on little sleep!), and so Guava Vitamin C Bright-Eye Gel Cream was born. ✨ With a a 10% vitamin C blend and 3% niacinamide blend to brighten dark circles, green caffeine and quinoa peptides to depuff, and hyaluronic acid to hydrate, Guava Eye is packed with beneficial ingredients that transform the eye area and create a smooth, seamless base for eye makeup. Keep watching to see more of Guava Eye’s background story and tips from founders @sarah_glow and @christine_glow on how to use in your everyday routine. ⁠
Available on glowrecipe.com, @sephora, and @sephoracanada. Check out other launch dates at the "Guava Eye" highlight on our page 💖⁠
#GlowRecipe #CrueltyFree #GuavaEye⁠
New! Watermelon Glow AHA Night Treatment 🌙 All of your questions answered

How do you layer Glow Recipe skincare? Press play as we walk you through it all, and find the TL;DR below:⁠
✨ All of our formulations are made to work in the same routine together, but if you're starting to introduce a new active ingredient into your routine, take it slow and gentle (everyone's skin is different!)⁠
✨ Here's the general flow of your routine: Cleansing Balm > Water-based Cleanse > Wash-Off Mask (a few times a week!) > Toner > Eye Cream > Serums > Moisturizer > SPF during the day or an Overnight Treatment at night⁠
✨ If you're using a few products in the same category, apply from thinnest to thickest⁠
Any questions? Drop them below!⁠
Glow Recipe Skincare is available @sephora, @sephoracanada, @cultbeauty, @meccabeauty, @sephoramiddleeast, @sephorasg, @sephoramy, @sephorahk, and @douglas_cosmetics⁠

How to Talk About Mental Health with @rarebeauty #BeautyCares

How is your skin feeling today? Chances are, there’s more than one concern it wants you to address. All of our serums were formulated to work together, so you can layer and tackle all of those concerns at once. Try using your favorite serum with the Strawberry Smooth AHA+BHA Salicylic Serum for an extra blemish-fighting boost.⁠
✨ For redness & sensitivity: Avocado Ceramide Recovery Serum + Strawberry Smooth AHA+BHA Salicylic Serum targets texture and helps calm irritation⁠
✨ For dullness & dehydration: Guava Vitamin C Dark Spot Serum + Strawberry Smooth AHA+BHA Salicylic Serum helps brighten and soothe skin⁠
✨ For congestion & dryness: Plum Plump Hyaluronic Serum + Strawberry Smooth AHA+BHA Salicylic Serum deeply hydrates and helps control excess oil production
Available @sephora, @sephoracanada, and @cultbeauty
#GlowRecipe #CrueltyFree

We’re all about keeping pores happy and healthy, but traditional blemish treatments can be super drying, sticky, and irritating. That’s why we worked with our labs to create a clarifying serum that’s potent yet gentle enough for all skin, even sensitive. Keep watching to hear more of what inspired our co-founders @sarah_glow and @christine_glow to create the Strawberry Smooth AHA+BHA Salicylic Serum⁠
Strawberry Smooth BHA+AHA Salicylic Serum is now available @sephora, @sephoracanada, and glowrecipe.com. Check out our 🍓 highlight to see other launch dates⁠
#GlowRecipe #CrueltyFree #StrawberrySmooth

Smooth texture, treat and prevent breakouts, and refine pores while calming skin with the new Strawberry Smooth BHA+BHA Salicylic Acid Serum. Use this gentle clarifying serum in your daily routine as your serum step (after cleansing and toning, and before moisturizer), and, yes, it pairs well with our other serums so you can mix and match in the same routine to target multiple skin concerns.⁠
Available @sephora, @sephoracanada, and glowrecipe.com today. Check out our 🍓 highlight to see other launch dates⁠

If you’re not using the 3 Skin Method… you’re missing out on one of Korean skincare's best-kept hydration secrets 🍉💧

Straight from Korean skincare philosophy, this method is all about layering your toner *three times* right after cleansing to deeply hydrate, balance, and prep your skin. It’s like pressing in three layers of glow ✨

Our go-to? Watermelon Glow PHA+BHA Pore-Tight Toner—because it’s not just hydrating, it’s *pore refining* too:
🍉 Watermelon Extract to soothe and nourish
🌿 PHA + BHA to gently exfoliate
💧 Hyaluronic Acid to pull in moisture and keep it locked in

After each layer, gently pat into damp skin and let it soak in before applying the next. Your skin will feel bouncier, glowier, and more prepped for the rest of your routine.

One method, three layers, endless glow. Have you tried it yet? 👇
